Dear instagram support team 

Hey Instagram, You recently suspended my accounts @mercedeszz00 @sadiees._  @itsbenzzworld, and @sadies2.0 and I’m reaching out because I genuinely believe this was a mistake. I have reviewed your Community Guidelines and Terms of Use, and to the best of my knowledge, I did not violate any of them. I use both of these accounts for creative content, personal expression, and to connect with my audience in a positive and respectful way. I’ve always tried to follow the rules and contribute to the community in a way that’s uplifting and authentic. I was never given a clear reason for the suspension, which has left me confused and frustrated. I received no warning, and I wasn’t notified of any specific post or activity that supposedly violated your policies. I put a lot of time and effort into building these profiles, and losing access without explanation has really impacted me — not just emotionally, but also in terms of my creative work and communication with others. If there was truly something wrong, I’d like to understand what it was so I can fix it and make sure it doesn’t happen again. But if there was no actual violation, then I kindly ask that you restore both accounts as soon as possible. I value the platform and what it offers, and I’d love the chance to continue being a part of the Instagram community. Thank you for your time, and I hope to hear from you soon.
